    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not the kind of rest i mean. i mean i'm so tired of fighting it. every morning i wake up and i just wish i hadn't. it feels like i'm just dragging this massive thing behind me and there's no point to any of it anymore. do you think people really just... find a way to stop feeling things like this?",
